                Trailer Online is easy to use and has served my business well over the past 4 years. 
                <p>Stan, <a target="_blank" href="http://broweronline.com">Brower Online, Bradenton FL</a></p>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote>
                I don't know much about computers, but I knew we needed a website. Small Business Online
                was very patient and easy to work with.
                <p>Jake, <a target="_blank" href="http://capitaltrailerhelena.com">Capital Trailer, Helena MT</a></p>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <div class="large-6 large-pull-6 columns pad">
        <h2>Small Business Online</h2>
        <p>
            We specialize in developing software for small business and government agencies. 
            Our experienced staff will assist you at any point along your project from concept ideation to installing software on servers. 
        </p>
        
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
            We strive to create high-quality software to solve complex business problems while remaining within budget and time constraints.
        </p>

        <h3>Our Process</h3>
        <p>
            We keep costs down and quality high by following an agile project methodology. 
        </p>

        <h4>Envision</h4>
        <p>
            Project are conceived from visions of the future. Understanding that vision is critical to the success of your project.
        </p>

        <h4>Design</h4>
        <p>
            Graphic designers and html developers work with you to create a semi-functional prototype of the website. 
            The website looks finished, but it does not manage data. 
        </p>

        <h4>Develop</h4>
        <p>
            Programmers add code to the prototype bring the screens to life with real data and business rules. 
        </p>
        
        <h4>Deploy</h4>
        <p>
            The functional website is deployed to hosting servers, and your project is completed.
        </p>

        <h4>Support</h4>
        <p>
            The developers who created the solution are available to fix bugs or make enhancements.
        </p>
        

